OL,6,F"This meant that the driver did not
OL,7,Fhave access to equipment on the
OL,8,Ftrain's underframe, including the
OL,9,Fsander test button. Consequently,
OL,10,Fcertain safety systems, including the
OL,11,Foperation of the automatic sanding
OL,12,Fsystem, could not be checked."
OL,14,FTransport For Wales had said these
OL,15,Fwere additional assurance checks, and
OL,16,Fnot mandatory
