OL,6,FFollowing the crash, Network Rail said
OL,7,Fone of its railhead treatment trains `
OL,8,Fwhich tackle autumn leaf fall ` ran
OL,9,Falong the line and passing loop the
OL,10,Fnight before the crash.
OL,12,FThe RAIB said its investigation will
OL,13,Fconsider several aspects, such as the
OL,14,Fsanding systems and the cause and
OL,15,Fseverity of low adhesion at Talerddig.
OL,17,FTransport for Wales and Network Rail
OL,18,Fsay they are fulling cooperating with
OL,19,Fthe investigation. In a joint
OL,20,Fstatement they said:
